Package it.unicam.cs.pa.jbudget105053.model

Class BasicMovement

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unicam.cs.pa.jbudget105053.model.BasicMovement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasID, Movement
    public class BasicMovement
extends java.lang.Object
implements Movement
    This class implements the interface Movement and has the responsibility of managing a single basic movement. It allows to get the information related to the movement: ID, type of movement, money amount, date, associated account, associated transaction and the list of all the tags associated with the movement. Each movement derives its date from the transaction it is associated with.
    Author:
    Tommaso Catervi
